<paragraph blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Morphology — Male: Integument papillate (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7B</figureCitation>
). Posteromedial margin of Cx-I broadly rounded. Cx-IV with a distinct nose-like protruding medial margin. Genital plate anterior margin with a small knob-shaped medial projection projecting in a deep indentation, posterior margin deeply indented with a small protrusion in the centre of indentation; acetabula in a triangular arrangement, Ac-2 and Ac- 3 on the same level (
<figureCitation box="[1067,1188,677,701]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7A</figureCitation>
). P-2 ventral margin proximally almost straight, distoventrally protruding in a long and slender projection, apically covered by a few small denticles; P-3 distally with 7- 8 larger denticles covering more than half of ventral margin (
<figureCitation box="[970,1078,852,876]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figures 7</figureCitation>
E-F); P-4 slender, ventral setae close to each other (separation 22 µm).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Measurements — Idiosoma L/W 713/637; coxal field L/W 331/522, Cx-III W 406; genital plate L/W 166/213, ratio 0.78; ejaculatory complex L 132. Palp: total L 378, dL/H, dL/H ratio: P-1, 30/36, 0.83; P- 2, 97/65, 1.5; P-3, 77/57, 1.35; P-4, 126/31, 4.1; P- 5, 48/16, 2.9; L ratio P-2/P-4, 0.77; chelicera total L 254, claw L 90, basal segment L 170, L basal segment/claw ratio 1.9. Legs: dL of I-L-5-6 (
<figureCitation box="[1298,1417,1183,1207]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7C</figureCitation>
): 135, 130; dL of IV-L: 113, 94, 131, 194, 213, 163.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
